<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DOL Linear - English Center | Chọn Đúng Khóa, Lên Band Mục Tiêu</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --dol-red: #E31818;
            --dol-red-hover: #C91212;
            --dol-dark: #1E293B;
            --dol-gray-bg: #F8FAFC;
            --dol-border: #E2E8F0;
            --text-secondary: #64748B;
            --radius-lg: 24px;
            --radius-md: 16px;
            --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'SF Pro Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: var(--dol-dark);
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Top Bar Thông Báo */
        .top-notification {
            background-color: #FFF0F0;
            color: var(--dol-red);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #FFE0E0;
        }

        /* Header Navigation */
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 18px 8%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .logo-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: var(--dol-red);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(227, 24, 24, 0.15);
        }
        .logo-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .logo-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #0F172A;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        .logo-sub {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--dol-red);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .nav-item > a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #334155;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: var(--transition);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .nav-item:hover > a {
            color: var(--dol-red);
            background-color: var(--dol-gray-bg);
        }

        .header-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .btn-test-nhanh {
            border: 2px solid var(--dol-red);
            color: var(--dol-red);
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .btn-test-nhanh:hover {
            background-color: #FFF0F0;
        }
        .btn-dang-ky-tv {
            background-color: var(--dol-red);
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 12px 26px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(227, 24, 24, 0.15);
        }
        .btn-dang-ky-tv:hover {
            background-color: var(--dol-red-hover);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 80px 8%;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            gap: 60px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hero-content {
            flex: 1.1;
            min-width: 320px;
        }

        .ai-badge {
            background-color: #FFF0F0;
            color: var(--dol-red);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 800;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            border: 1px solid #FFE0E0;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.2;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #0F172A;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 45px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .btn-hero-red {
            background-color: var(--dol-red);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(227, 24, 24, 0.2);
        }
        .btn-hero-red:hover {
            background-color: var(--dol-red-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .btn-hero-white {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid var(--dol-border);
            color: #334155;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .btn-hero-white:hover {
            border-color: var(--dol-red);
            color: var(--dol-red);
        }

        /* Khối thống kê mini */
        .hero-stats-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            padding-top: 30px;
        }
        .stat-box-mini {
            background: var(--dol-gray-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            padding: 16px 24px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            flex: 1;
        }
        .stat-box-mini strong {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #0F172A;
            display: block;
        }
        .stat-box-mini span {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Banner bên phải */
        .hero-visual {
            flex: 0.9;
            min-width: 380px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .visual-card-wrapper {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 32px;
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
        }
        .visual-card-wrapper img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: block;
        }
        .ai-tutor-tag {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -25px;
            left: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            display: flex;
            align-items: start;
            gap: 14px;
        }
        .ai-tutor-icon {
            width: 38px;
            height: 38px;
            background-color: var(--dol-red);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* Khóa học trọng tâm */
        .courses-section {
            padding: 100px 8%;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        .center-title-box {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 60px auto;
        }
        .sub-badge {
            color: var(--dol-red);
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: block;
        }
        .center-title-box h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #0F172A;
        }
        .courses-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }
        .course-card {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 30px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .course-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: var(--dol-red);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(227, 24, 24, 0.04);
        }
        .course-icon-box {
            width: 46px;
            height: 46px;
            background-color: #FFF0F0;
            color: var(--dol-red);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* KHUNG CHÈN VIDEO YOUTUBE MỚI THÊM TẠI ĐÂY */
        .video-section {
            padding: 60px 8% 100px 8%;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .video-wrapper {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(227, 24, 24, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* Tỉ lệ màn hình 16:9 chuẩn */
            height: 0;
        }
        .video-wrapper iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: 0;
        }

        /* Ứng dụng trắc nghiệm nhanh */
        .quick-test-section {
            background-color: #FFF5F5;
            padding: 100px 8%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .test-app-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            padding: 40px;
            text-shadow: none;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
        }
        .test-progress {
            height: 6px;
            background-color: var(--dol-gray-bg);
            border-radius: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .test-progress-bar {
            height: 100%;
            width: 35%;
            background-color: var(--dol-red);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .options-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 24px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .option-item {
            background: var(--dol-gray-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .option-item:hover {
            border-color: var(--dol-red);
            background-color: #FFF0F0;
        }
        .option-item.correct {
            border-color: #28a745;
            background-color: #e6f4ea;
            color: #137333;
        }
        .test-result-box {
            display: none;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Bento Grid Layout */
        .bento-section {
            background-color: var(--dol-gray-bg);
            padding: 100px 8%;
        }
        .bento-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .bento-card {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 40px;
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
        }
        .bento-card.double-width {
            grid-column: span 2;
        }
        .bento-card h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        .bento-card p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Khung phản hồi sinh viên chạy ngang */
        .marquee-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .marquee-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            width: max-content;
            animation: marqueeContinuous 25s linear infinite;
        }
        .marquee-wrapper:hover { animation-play-state: paused; }
        .fb-marquee-card {
            background: var(--dol-gray-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 25px;
            width: 350px;
        }
        .fb-user-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .fb-avatar {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            background-color: var(--dol-red);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        @keyframes marqueeContinuous {
            0% { transform: translateX(0); }
            100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
        }

        /* Biểu mẫu đăng ký */
        .register-section {
            padding: 100px 8%;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--dol-gray-bg);
        }
        .form-container {
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 45px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }
        .form-container input, .form-container select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            background-color: var(--dol-gray-bg);
            outline: none;
        }
        .form-container input:focus { border-color: var(--dol-red); background-color: white; }
        .form-container button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px;
            background-color: var(--dol-red);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .form-container button:hover { background-color: var(--dol-red-hover); }

        /* Chatbox AI */
        .chat-widget-container {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 35px;
            right: 35px;
            z-index: 2000;
        }
        .chat-btn-toggle {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: var(--dol-red);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-size: 26px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(227, 24, 24, 0.3);
        }
        .chat-window {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 75px;
            right: 0;
            width: 350px;
            height: 450px;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            border: 1px solid var(--dol-border);
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .chat-header {
            background-color: var(--dol-red);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .chat-messages-box {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            background-color: var(--dol-gray-bg);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .msg-bubble { padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 14px; font-size: 14px; max-width: 80%; line-height: 1.4; }
        .msg-bubble.bot { background: white; border: 1px solid var(--dol-border); align-self: flex-start; border-top-left-radius: 4px; }
        .msg-bubble.user { background: var(--dol-red); color: white; align-self: flex-end; border-top-right-radius: 4px; }
        .chat-footer-input { display: flex; padding: 12px; border-top: 1px solid var(--dol-border); background: white; }
        .chat-footer-input input { flex: 1; border: none; padding: 10px; background: var(--dol-gray-bg); border-radius: 8px; outline: none; font-weight: 600; }
        .chat-footer-input button { background: none; border: none; color: var(--dol-red); font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; padding: 0 12px; }

        footer {
            background-color: var(--dol-dark);
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 60px 8%;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-top: 5px solid var(--dol-red);
        }

        @media (max-width: 968px) {
            .hero-section { padding: 40px 5%; text-align: center; }
            .hero-content h1 { font-size: 36px; }
            .hero-stats-row { justify-content: center; }
            .bento-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .bento-card.double-width { grid-column: span 1; }
            header nav { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <a href="#" class="logo-container">
            <div class="logo-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i></div>
            <div class="logo-text">
                <span class="logo-title">DOL Linear</span>
                <span class="logo-sub">English Center</span>
            </div>
        </a>
        <nav>
            <div class="nav-item"><a href="#courses">Khóa học</a></div>
            <div class="nav-item"><a href="#">LinearThinking</a></div>
            <div class="nav-item"><a href="#quickTestSection">Test miễn phí</a></div>
        </nav>
        <div class="header-actions">
            <a href="#quickTestSection" class="btn-test-nhanh">Test nhanh</a>
            <a href="#registerSection" class="btn-dang-ky-tv">Đăng ký tư vấn</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="ai-badge">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i> Cá nhân hóa lộ trình bằng AI + LinearThinking
            </div>
            
            <h1>Chọn đúng khóa, rút ngắn đường đến band mục tiêu</h1>
            
            <p>Nền tảng luyện IELTS, TOEIC, SAT và tiếng Anh giao tiếp theo phương pháp LinearThinking: hiểu logic đề, xử lý nhanh, sửa lỗi tận gốc và có AI tutor theo sát mỗi ngày.</p>
            
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <div class="hero-btns">
                    <a href="#quickTestSection" class="btn-hero-red">Đăng ký test trình độ miễn phí ➔</a>
                    <a href="#registerSection" class="btn-hero-white">Hỏi AI tư vấn lộ trình 🤖</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-stats-row">
                <div class="stat-box-mini">
                    <strong>40.000+</strong>
                    <span>học viên đã học</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box-mini">
                    <strong>7.5+</strong>
                    <span>mục tiêu IELTS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box-mini">
                    <strong>1-1</strong>
                    <span>chữa bài cá nhân</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="hero-visual">
            <div class="visual-card-wrapper">
                <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5e7300f2e043186fa884be5e/1601362624508-41K0B36Y72WOKT2YAGY8/LOGO+DOL+IELTS+DINH+LUC+RGB+01.png" alt="DOL Linear">
            </div>
            <div class="ai-tutor-tag">
                <div class="ai-tutor-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-robot"></i></div>
                <div>
                    <strong style="font-size:14px; display:block; color:#0F172A;">AI Tutor vừa phân tích</strong>
                    <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-secondary); margin-top:2px;">Bạn mạnh ở Vocabulary, cần tăng Reading inference. Gợi ý: học IELTS Foundation 6 tuần + mini test mỗi ngày.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="courses-section" id="courses">
        <div class="center-title-box">
            <span class="sub-badge">Khóa học trọng tâm</span>
            <h2>Chọn đúng mục tiêu. Học đúng lộ trình.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="courses-grid">
            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="course-icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i></div>
                <h3>IELTS Linear</h3>
                <p>Từ mất gốc đến 7.5+, tập trung Reading logic, Listening keywords, Speaking framework và Writing chữa chi tiết 1-1.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="course-icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-headphones"></i></div>
                <h3>TOEIC Sprint</h3>
                <p>Lộ trình bứt phá điểm số nhanh 450-850+, tối ưu chiến thuật nghe bắt từ khóa, xử lý bẫy ngữ pháp và quản trị thời gian.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="course-icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-square-root-variable"></i></div>
                <h3>SAT Mastery</h3>
                <p>Reading & Writing theo cấu trúc lập luận tư duy tuyến tính, Math theo dạng bài, phù hợp định học bổng du học.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="video-section">
        <div class="center-title-box">
            <span class="sub-badge">Video phương pháp</span>
            <h2>Vượt Qua Nỗi Sợ IELTS Cùng LinearThinking</h2>
